          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-1" n="1">The sage, who said he should be proud</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-2" n="2">Of windows in his breast;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-3" n="3">Because he ne'er one thought allow'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-4" n="4">That might not be confest:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-5" n="5">His window scrawl'd by ev'ry rake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-6" n="6">His breast again would cover,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-7" n="7">And fairly bid the D────l take</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-55B--line-8" n="8">The di'mond and the lover.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
